Product description

Size:Pack of 24  |  Color:Assorted

High-performance colored pencils are water-soluble and easy to blend, for an unlimited range of shades. Durable Anti-Break-System protects lead center, making pencil up to 30% stronger. Pencils won't roll off the table or work surface with classic hexagonal shape. Vibrant color coating provides easier identification and color differentiation.

      I really like these!

      Having only just got them in the post I can only comment on my first impressions and testing them on my adult colouring book - Harry Potter.

      For 5.99 you get 24 colours. I was surprised to see that there were a nice range in this collection. Pencils are easy to hold and found that they were good quality. You don't have to press so hard to get a good shade. Literally the lightest touch will do, which is what makes these pencils so comfortable.

      I did try using colouring pens but found they bled too much through the page, which, unfortunately, ruined the first few pages. However, pencils seemed like the better option and I was right.
